NAME
	temple

DESCRIPTION
	Temple of the mighty god of thieves, Skert, is an important place
	for us thieves. Every thief can pray there and hope for a special
	blessing from Skert, also thieves can 'sacrifice' things for
	experience, and lay dead ones to rest with 'cremate' command.

	The temple is also the front entrance to the Guild.

